Quickstrike:





Quickstrike was relieved to get back to the cave without incident. He was 
glad that Wrath hadn't brought back his Maximal comrades to get revenge on 
an unfair fight.

He turned, with Stingtra still in his arms, checking just in case. All was 
quiet and black. The stars shined just perfectly with the moon.

He walked to the CR chamber, then paused. He tried to open it with Stingtra 
still in his arms, but he couldn't manage, not both with his bizare arms and 
hands. He gently put her down, resting her at the side of the chamber, then 
pressed a botton that openeded it. He stepped back to the side and picked 
Stingtra up, placing her in the chamber. He closed it.
